<br>
I do see that there is a fundamental difference.  There is a set of rules for one mob and not another.  The formality you talk of would then mean that ANY mob in the game could be considered a rotation mob minus the technicality of a link on a page.  <br>
<br>
The fundamental difference is there doesn't seem to be a logical reason to make these mobs rotation mobs as has been discussed at length by me and several other people in this thread.  The only logical reason I can see to make these mobs rotational mobs is to opress a very large population of this server.<br>
<br>
